<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>게임 베타테스트</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <header>
        <h1>Block Block</h1>
      </header>

      <main>
        <section class="download-section">
          <h2>최신 버전 다운로드</h2>
          <% if (version) { %>
          <p>버전: <%= version.version %></p>
          <a href="/games/<%= version.filename %>" class="btn download-btn">
            다운로드
          </a>
          <% } else { %>
          <p>현재 다운로드 가능한 버전이 없습니다.</p>
          <% } %>
        </section>

        <section class="feedback-section">
          <h2>피드백</h2>
          <p>베타테스트에 참여하시고 피드백을 남겨주세요!</p>
          <a href="/feedback" class="btn">피드백 게시판 가기</a>
        </section>
      </main>

      <footer>
        <small>&copy; 2025 Block Block. All rights reserved.</small>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
